These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: corn, pepper, potato
House: cottage, cape-cod, modern
City: boston, paris, new-york
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bike, bus
1. the person eating pepper is between the cottage house and the person driving the car##2
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the person eating potato is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the cottage house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food          | corn      | pepper        | potato     |
| House         | modern | cape-cod | cottage    |
| City   | paris   | boston       | new-york |
| Transport         | car  | bike      | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, coach, photographer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, classical, ambient
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, blend, bluemaster
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, tea
1. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the fan of classical is the coach##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the coach is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the photographer##3
6. the photographer is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking tea is between the fan of classical and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | coach    | photographer | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | classical | punk       | ambient   |
| Cigar           | bluemaster  | blend   | prince     |
| Beverage         | soy-milk | tea       | water   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, rugby, skiing
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer, manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, amber, apricot
1. the manager is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who likes apricot##2
5. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
6. the manager is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Sport   | skiing     | cycling | rugby |
| Job           | freelancer       | software-developer   | manager    |
| Color     | apricot      | azure   | amber |

