.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
City: marseilles, paris, berlin
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, golf, badminton
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, mystery
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, orange, corn
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person eating orange is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| City         | paris  | marseilles       | berlin |
| Sport           | badminton     | golf      | rugby   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | mystery     |
| Food   | pumpkin      | corn   | orange     |

