.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, water
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry, plum
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, zombie, action
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, blue, blood-red
1. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
6. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Food           | pomegranate | raspberry | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | zombie   | family            |
| Color   | blue   | blood-red  | grey         |

