There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, red, light-blue
1. the person drinking water is between the photographer and the person traveling to hamburg##2
2. the person who likes brown is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes red is on the left of the social-worker##1
5. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| City          | miami    | venice     | hamburg |
| Job           | photographer | social-worker | doctor      |
| Beverage   | fanta      | water       | mirinda    |
