.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, lily
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, zombie
3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, bridge
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, turkish
1. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is the canadian##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person who growslily is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person playing monopoly is between the canadian and the person who growszinnia##2
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Flower          | zinnia | poppy | lily |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action    | zombie |
| Game   | scrabble  | monopoly   | bridge    |
| Nationality     | turkish   | japanese       | canadian |

