.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, march, january
There 3 different types of food: banana, corn, cucumber
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, surfing
1. the person eating cucumber is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person eating corn##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating corn and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| Birthday         | january        | october   | march   |
| Food   | cucumber       | banana    | corn |
| Sport     | surfing          | parkour | sailing       |

