.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, backgammon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, disco, punk
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, electrician, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, october, august
1. the electrician is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
3. the software-developer is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the electrician is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the software-developer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Game          | billiard  | monopoly   | backgammon      |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | punk      | blues      |
| Job   | mechanic | electrician | software-developer    |
| Birthday           | august   | october     | march |

