.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, teacher
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, almond-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, reading, baking
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, avocado, lemon
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the person drinking milk is the dancer##1
3. the teacher is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
6. the dancer is in an odd position##4
7. the dancer is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Job           | dancer     | teacher    | freelancer |
| Beverage   | milk  | cola | almond-milk      |
| Hobby   | baking       | reading   | dancing    |
| Food     | avocado | lemon        | pumpkin     |

