.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, jet-ski
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, october, november
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, go
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing poker##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Transport      | jet-ski     | snowmobile      | taxi  |
| Birthday          | october     | november | april       |
| Game   | poker  | go    | scrabble      |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton  | snowboarding |

