.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
City: berlin, san-francisco, liverpool
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
3 different games are played: go, bridge, billiard
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to berlin and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City      | liverpool       | san-francisco   | berlin |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Game           | go      | bridge | billiard    |
| Flower         | poppy  | marigold     | tulip |

