.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, horse
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, lime, corn
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating corn##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating corn##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | hamster   | horse |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Beverage         | water    | almond-milk | lemonade   |
| Food     | lime  | corn     | artichoke  |

