.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, havana, blend
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, tram, snowmobile
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, february
1. the american is the blend-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person driving the snowmobile and the alhambra-smoker##2
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar         | blend    | havana   | alhambra      |
| Transport           | snowmobile | ship    | tram |
| Nationality   | american       | argentine | turkish      |
| Birthday         | february         | december   | april     |

