There are 3 different nationalities: french, brazilian, russian
3 different pets are kept: dog, pony, rat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, western, musical
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, bolivar
1. the person watching western movies is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the french is in an even position##4
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the brazilian##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality        | brazilian | french | russian |
| Pet         | dog       | pony    | rat       |
| Movie-Genre       | western  | musical | zombie      |
| Cigar   | bolivar      | ritmeester    | dannemann |

