House: victorian, colonial, farmhouse
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, pakistani
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, bridge
1. the victorian house is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to new-york and the person playing bridge##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| City          | san-francisco     | boston | new-york   |
| House         | farmhouse   | victorian | colonial |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch       | colombian   |
| Game     | bridge     | scrabble  | poker        |

