3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
