.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, yellow, grey
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, bellflower, orchid
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, zombie, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who likes grey##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsazalea is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes yellow is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Color          | yellow  | chestnut   | grey |
| Flower   | bellflower      | orchid      | azalea   |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | fantasy | zombie |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket   | rugby   |

