.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, german, polish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, february
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, lily, orchid
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the german##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growslily##1
5. the polish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the polish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Nationality           | chinese  | polish | german   |
| Birthday   | june | february           | april      |
| Flower           | orchid   | lily          | sunflower |
| Transport     | boat    | tram           | snowmobile |

 